OL,3,CMan named following fatal A75 crash
OL,4,Cnear Glenluce
OL,6,FThe man who died following a collision
OL,7,Fon the near Glenluce has been named as
OL,8,FKevin Bodle.
OL,10,FThe 49-year-old was pronounced dead
OL,11,Fafter the two-vehicle crash at around
OL,12,F6:45am on Tuesday 21 May 2024.
OL,14,FIt involved a white Peugeot Partner
OL,15,Fvan and a stationary Volvo paver
OL,16,Fmachine.JMr Bodle, the driver of the
OL,17,FPeugeot, was taken to Galloway
OL,18,FCommunity Hospital, where he was later
OL,19,Fpronounced dead.
