OL,6,FSergeant Lloyd Caven said: "Our
OL,7,Fthoughts remain with Kevin's family
OL,8,Fand friends at this terrible time, as
OL,9,Fthey try to come to terms with their
OL,10,Floss.
OL,12,F"We continue to appeal for anyone with
OL,13,Finformation on the crash, any
OL,14,Fwitnesses, or motorists who may have
OL,15,Fbeen in the area and have dashcam
OL,16,Ffootage, to please come forward."
OL,18,FEnquiries into the full circumstances
OL,19,Fremain ongoing.
